{% block title %}Tournaments{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<h2 class="sports">Tournaments</h2>

<div class="row content-row">
	<h3 class="sports">Kingdom of Sports will be running social team tournaments.</h3><br/>
	
	<h4 class="sports">So Sign up Now</h4><br/>
	<p class="sports">
	The Tournament will be run on a league basis with the top four teams making the playoffs!<br/>
	
